; ---- Seam markers ----
; 2-px-wide ember-orange vertical lines at each chunk boundary so the
; chunk-seam is unmistakable in HTML5 soak screenshots. If z-index ordering
; misbehaves under gl_compatibility, the seam markers will visibly drop
; below the chunk floor at the boundary.

